  "description": "A wide-angle view of a rocky beach with dark, wet stones and sand covering the foreground. The beach extends towards the ocean, where gentle waves roll in. Large, dark rock formations jut out from the shoreline and stand in the shallow water. In the distance, a coastline is visible, with hills and vegetation partially obscured by a hazy, overcast sky. The sky is mostly blue with patches of white and grey clouds. The scene appears peaceful and natural, suggesting a remote coastal environment. There is a hint of a figure in the distance on the left side of the photo.",
